{
  "stem": "22586.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were given, I remember, a bucket of soup with no utensils, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But somebody had a spoon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And about 20 or so women had to share the soup, so everybody would have a spoonful.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we would go around, because, God forbid, somebody would have more than the other.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That way, we made sure that everybody had their share.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then, a day-- a few days later, some of the girls came down with typhoid fever or typhus.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm not really sure which one it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And-- but there, we were taken to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we worked at the railroad station, cleaning up debris from bombing that they had.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And here we finally had some kind of [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] facility to shower.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was outdoors.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But we had water, which we didn't have in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In fact, in Auschwitz, even when you had to go to the bathroom-- to the latrine, not bathroom, latrine, we would-- we would be taken there.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We'd be allowed a certain amount of time, maybe five minutes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And finished or not, you left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And no toilet paper.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] But in Gelsenkirchen, or Gelsenberg, at least we had something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We had water.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we had facilities.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were in Gelsenkirchen from the beginning of July.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I can't recall when it was, but one day some-- about four or five men came from Essen, Germany, from the Krupp ammunition factory.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they picked out again women, that there were about 500 of us who they wanted to come and work for the ammunition factory in Essen.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
